{"tid":1869422,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為旗下海思晶片被發現有後門，可入侵網路攝影機","createTime":"2020-02-08T07:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T05:23:20.000Z","uid":12628,"like":97,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"087921f9071feb9c12894c1ae1c1af19f83d23ac","tid":1869422,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"華為旗下海思晶片被發現有後門，可入侵網路攝影機<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/18/225347_7e2a96be9717a91eddbc0f1da1d2d192.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2F225347_7e2a96be9717a91eddbc0f1da1d2d192.png&h=afa6429c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/18/225348_a8f3cef86477efb6875167d9e6b9ce88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2F225348_a8f3cef86477efb6875167d9e6b9ce88.png&h=3e728e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/18/225349_cf5d8c68703114490a63ed1acdd6f45e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2F225349_cf5d8c68703114490a63ed1acdd6f45e.png&h=9d6848be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/06/phpUhZXmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F06%2FphpUhZXmN.jpg&h=f2deba50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少國家仍然在研究是否封鎖華為的 5G 設備，以保障國家安全，不過華為除了 5G 設備有安全風險，旗下海思晶片最近也被發現有後門，可直接存取使用晶片的網路攝影機等產品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安全研究人員 Vladislav Yarmak 稍早發現，海思 SoC 晶片系統韌體有個遙距除錯和管理工具，可存取同個網路的攝影機和閉路電視等，就是刻意留存的後門。只要有人連接特定端口 TCP 9530，並請求 Telnet 連接，就可以使用非常簡單的 root 帳號和 123456 密碼（或其他 5 個簡單的固定密碼）登入，並擁有 superuser 權限，直接存取和控制裝置。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員表示，這個後門至少存在於使用 hi3518 SoC 晶片的大量網路攝影機和閉路電視產品，不過這個端口只向本地網路開放，而不是向網際網路開放，但仍是潛在的危險。而華為和海思暫時未回應此新聞。"},{"pid":"40966c3bb0f2f5adf87c2aab6bd66e1b2c26d84f","tid":1869422,"uid":76899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"376f5c55f673ebb40285c06e24f89e15f85bf46c","tid":1869422,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"唔過兩頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a638d5189815cadaef7d29d09a1a976a6046654e","tid":1869422,"uid":117437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798286219091d9e159f7c08748d2d0577d0adc2e","tid":1869422,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"日落帝國R.A.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a32541e179ffab95e343b09d7be7d1f77c4836e","tid":1869422,"uid":194894,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"日落帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑鳩死,侵侵叫到唔好用佢就偏要用,呢鋪柒啦"},{"pid":"247628481de5b0921273ed3cecca1d6f85670ac7","tid":1869422,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:01:18.000Z","msg":"英國表示，有效率又平做乜唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7215e24aa4f83b254f108bea9732f2d4a1d5cf2","tid":1869422,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco